68},{"title":"PDF","target":"biblib/kenmoku_erinacol_2004/kenmoku_erinacol_2004.pdf","line":70}],"metadata":{"id":"kenmoku_erinacol_2004","type":"article-journal","title":"Erinacol (Cyatha-3,12-dien-14β-ol) and 11-O-Acetylcyathin A3, New Cyathane Metabolites from an Erinacine Q-Producing Hericium erinaceum","issued":{"date-parts":[[2004]]},"DOI":"10.1271/bbb.68.1786","container-title":"Bioscience, Biotechnology, and Biochemistry","abstract":"In our search for new cyathane metabolites related to the biosynthesis of erinacine Q in Hericium erinaceum, we isolated a novel cyatha-3,12-dien-14β-ol named erinacol together with known 11-O-acetylcyathatriol (the erinacine Q aglycon) and new metabolite 11-O-acetylcyathin A3 from the mycelial extract. The structure of each compound was determined by spectral methods. Possible biosynthetic relationships of these metabolites are discussed from their structural features.","tags":["#literature_note"],"author":[{"family":"Kenmoku","given":"Hiromichi","literal":""},{"family":"Kenmoku","given":"Hiromichi","literal":""},{"family":"Tanaka","given":"Kazumi","literal":""},{"family":"Tanaka","given":"Kazumi","literal":""},{"family":"Okada","given":"Katsuhide","literal":""},{"family":"Okada","given":"Katsuhide","literal":""},{"family":"Okada","given":"Katsuhide","literal":""},{"family":"Okada","given":"Katsuhide","literal":""},{"family":"Kato","given":"Nobuo","literal":""},{"family":"Kato","given":"Nobuo","literal":""},{"family":"Sassa","given":"Takeshi","literal":""},{"family":"Sassa","given":"Takeshi","literal":""}],"citation-key":"kenmoku_erinacol_2004","year":"2004","dateCreated":"2026-03-31","reading-status":"to-read","aliases":["Erinacol (Cyatha-3,12-dien-14β-ol) and 11-O-Acetylcyathin A3, New Cyathane Metabolites from an Erinacine Q-Producing Hericium erinaceum"],"author-links":["[[Author/Hiromichi Kenmoku]]","[[Author/Hiromichi Kenmoku]]","[[Author/Kazumi Tanaka]]","[[Author/Kazumi Tanaka]]","[[Author/Katsuhide Okada]]","[[Author/K